{"type":"message","id":"de82a7d5","parentId":"3c15b484","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:41:23.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering skills for document management**\n\nI need to think about what skills to apply for document management. Maybe using Feishu Docs for organizing and categorizing would work best. I should consider whether Feishu Bitable is more specific for my needs. Since the task is to search through documents and categorize them into Bitable, I think I should choose Feishu Docs as the most suitable option. However, I should also remember to review the necessary skills before replying to any requests.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0ca5b223d5a1af220169b19b2f4280819185811a044ab09fe9\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsZsyT5hLtbeEQs3IOwgafht_rHOV1Rb7viHxJwZV7dBX-m25KgXr1x8tBXoEbbPG1VnoyRcIsAzY-IPVd-O0yaQ0xM4o-hb3SeWQtTRaBbmPYbiuiKdHei--K50oPQfpIeMA9F0Wv2DrnNl6yBZRqbx3yldwn7hoeigTcLvyaHGvPTHiR7JAY_c1vSKY7hzGulw0cpHNXxPdSUfMVrblodMoREEMPdy-y5C2LbuSIdBA-fq5Hdg1Az4eKNs_Sp429bDpkgjBnjWmGx1v1y_vlaGG6zCSv7hKe91zmp_L58CW1AFMxXbJzxYk74VrtJMor-hFpBUQF4TjbulOTcbNFKBoQQ3GiKQmyq6obakrymPBf3BP4SrUoZtr6pL5gfH32Is5tMgtNFw0KztY47eNZv0tfVbccqTTZEAS17VfMxCdbg1OiXs-Y_f_Umm8IO5IyOpj6i_At9CXouicJPUXvQb6J0S9ckZaBkwEbR4II5KemrDCwnQiqbyEbsUoRvjOlOSLYlns2alGoHEfjI5Cq-0go4Hj_GZVWYXjHvYvYb42eppU29ot6PPJ_tjYIEwi2nln0e0ktj9bssr9KV0uc2qJQ1GOBJMskVk70V_gKKdVvpomU4v5pGfzIyfvUSfFfasHCr0oBu25U8WBlngNFRRLBrxirN1VQ5fP2wUkdESm8oQHdvZsMcgGK8nTrgtjbctJ89qEbub8Lj4j1wagCGaKuZLa4s8Uq3wKs-QbP_mDPPUQfBBu4okr08CqcpwgAQsY44aKFk2H5pe2KIPMoR71fwDO0vrSkM28OdYoB-UTPs1zs49UR7V_zd79jQI6ap0oc31rYNP0QtTxbzGnrWX4w_5C3rNF-DGHbBLEtg93QgQScYNDVRWm8ZO7e0nrXZLFIKsN3dBI-hhh92SgimRjpeWLM3NlwCITeopuB6zl7Ih0rVopHkaBVXWghfSaLvc5g08lzPRYzMWfyaduT3GVjKwVqj0SlR3Elxj0LG4gTiIudpllrJSnZKR0NjWUHnXH1SK_vsfV3Z-VzhgQ6NSUdovM6rjD5LSKBgJPXCaT2nZJ8ft0wzcMahHuKwwsz_ptTXW1UTgtc6rU26SVWPpfvscMaarTom9hGgf3vsgMvThkD4otmCHml9q94PpPZSS51QETHQ8Z6KNaPMHWppJTvgB4-yYPMrVH4QGmszUcOpDbaNgeRC71fD8-lzlIOBBgexkO_bFiT45eFMJSupN6fQ==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering skills for document management**\\n\\nI need to think about what skills to apply for document management. Maybe using Feishu Docs for organizing and categorizing would work best. I should consider whether Feishu Bitable is more specific for my needs. Since the task is to search through documents and categorize them into Bitable, I think I should choose Feishu Docs as the most suitable option. However, I should also remember to review the necessary skills before replying to any requests.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"行，那就全量扫。本王先把你能访问的飞书文档全捞出来，再建总表分类入库。","textSignature":"msg_0ca5b223d5a1af220169b19b32bf3081918b7834eea4ca228c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9I8gZFamLb8ASIk4AaQfIqVw|fc_0ca5b223d5a1af220169b19b32ccfc8191bf7061cd85f32c09","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.agents/skills/feishu-doc-1.2.7/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/suchuanlei/.agents/skills/feishu-doc-1.2.7/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":705,"output":147,"cacheRead":62336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63188,"cost":{"input":0.00123375,"output":0.002058,"cacheRead":0.0109088,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01420055}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773247271404}}
{"type":"message","id":"bfc6453b","parentId":"de82a7d5","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:41:23.304Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9I8gZFamLb8ASIk4AaQfIqVw|fc_0ca5b223d5a1af220169b19b32ccfc8191bf7061cd85f32c09","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-doc\ndescription: Fetch content from Feishu (Lark) Wiki, Docs, Sheets, and Bitable. Automatically resolves Wiki URLs to real entities and converts content to Markdown.\ntags: [feishu, lark, wiki, doc, sheet, document, reader, writer]\n---\n\n# Feishu Doc Skill\n\nFetch content from Feishu (Lark) Wiki, Docs, Sheets, and Bitable. Write and update documents.\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- Install `feishu-common` first.\n- This skill depends on `../feishu-common/index.js` for token and API auth.\n\n## Capabilities\n\n- **Read**: Fetch content from Docs, Sheets, Bitable, and Wiki.\n- **Create**: Create new blank documents.\n- **Write**: Overwrite document content with Markdown.\n- **Append**: Append Markdown content to the end of a document.\n- **Blocks**: List, get, update, and delete specific blocks.\n\n## Long Document Handling (Unlimited Length)\n\nTo generate long documents (exceeding LLM output limits of ~2000-4000 tokens):\n1. **Create** the document first to get a `doc_token`.\n2. **Chunk** the content into logical sections (e.g., Introduction, Chapter 1, Chapter 2).\n3. **Append** each chunk sequentially using `feishu_doc_append`.\n4. Do NOT try to write the entire document in one `feishu_doc_write` call if it is very long; use the append loop pattern.\n\n## Usage\n\n```bash\n# Read\nnode index.js --action read --token <doc_token>\n\n# Create\nnode index.js --action create --title \"My Doc\"\n\n# Write (Overwrite)\nnode index.js --action write --token <doc_token> --content \"# Title\\nHello world\"\n\n# Append\nnode index.js --action append --token <doc_token> --content \"## Section 2\\nMore text\"\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nCreate a `config.json` file in the root of the skill or set environment variables:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"app_id\": \"YOUR_APP_ID\",\n  \"app_secret\": \"YOUR_APP_SECRET\"\n}\n```\n\nEnvironment variables:\n- `FEISHU_APP_ID`\n- `FEISHU_APP_SECRET`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773247283300}}
