{"type":"message","id":"38df9a3e","parentId":"6d39b2fb","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:48:50.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering batch processing**\n\nI think I need to do seven more tasks, and it might be efficient to batch them together for parallel processing. I wonder if handling them in one go would save time and effort instead of doing them individually. I’ll look into how to set that up, ensuring everything flows smoothly. There’s a lot to think about regarding organization here. Let’s see if I can tackle this in a more streamlined way!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0ca5b223d5a1af220169b19cbfefd48191b8aaed522814129c\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsZzCY5gznuFf62yWxkTXIn_41Peh_s7GjKB1Ci6j6Y9HMVh5bzJYQ7bRi8iNCYTqdFLTwLd597VmixOZcihp8dLIaHjNRp6B7NsTFV8Vy4mDyHpoadxFMWkmGorBSwzypv0XLRb9FuisgE74Fz9bPSTK3AuzN9Z8KtrCT-2mcgprPnBYfssCszKKI-VxnAHiNiD6qBQ7Ukr3CY33wn74VqIpx6OUtnzWWmFvLRyuHdKAVH2jv4u_s7HV015i5kON4o76HeILKp6Kg1VgnJuNaKU7jlXrEAtQFIkCfxk7caBjR9YXc4vnYjTbMW3O5LNpU7B1EkoNeJzuuPiQCOK4v-Tk6IZGwPLyzHBBd5zyja-ICmJilGnVieIqJ_Iqz0t2PMFSZv_DG66QNNHtFF83_0F9dkCT0dTK2-8eM6furIzI7EjArxlWQNGVd38473ye2OiExjzdu1I9EWUyawBffEG3f6UKmLCxle2vXtTDZuQ6w6ayciW1ugiL6PGOiscAmwM3DmlwqegLYvvLoO5FVGZunuJV-nXs89MyI_qMio-fB4h9caRILL6P_LI7pxgWiHe_3k-e-ELSpX2T0m4aWzGe78cjlk-IVcTvRt_mE9sg3DE0u7nOsRHQqPB0aLf-jS2apK3UEVuBMP5Eu3VJUsRvRH9HnjM2Tcn3zAEU10fXa1hWu0l9h-6ETQ3HWDv6Mjqf0JoFOehRSYhzYfMoQA_l57tNcZSjQeUzyitWYO3d82goiED_Wa2JWYdsknoN1XSk63IstRWDqMu1XGGR-Vj7rdCIgEPMgfJ37If7n-a0WpFhlF0u6o1UvZSVkUjI_6k9ie58DJ1Ejopwit3BdQt9yE9tz6l5bUdlIDHa6fqq1S2-xkTMTbk7rA9gVYixVsEZ\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering batch processing**\\n\\nI think I need to do seven more tasks, and it might be efficient to batch them together for parallel processing. I wonder if handling them in one go would save time and effort instead of doing them individually. I’ll look into how to set that up, ensuring everyth