{"type":"message","id":"5eb22b11","parentId":"cd2d95a5","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:07:10.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，这版之前偏“记录”，不够“上台讲”。本王刚把它扩成讲课长稿版了，结构、方法论、案例、踩坑、结论都补齐了。\n\n还是这个文档，你刷新看：\n<https://www.feishu.cn/docx/Hxkrddm3CoKxdrxxjlxcL9cQngb>\n\n如果你还要更像正式分享，我下一步还能继续给你加两层：\n- **讲课版口语化表达**（更适合你现场讲）\n- **PPT大纲版**（直接拆成 8-12 页）","textSignature":"msg_0ca5b223d5a1af220169b1a13a626c8191bd6019d52ded7fc8"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":181,"output":147,"cacheRead":152960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153288,"cost":{"input":0.00031675,"output":0.002058,"cacheRead":0.026768,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029142750000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773248824216}}
